Rating: 4
Just had to throw in my four forks. Excellent! I use my own mix of herbes de provence. Here it is for anyone who might like to try it: 1 tablespoon (each) dried thyme, dried sweet marjoram, dried summer or winter savory, dried rosemary; 2 bay leaves, crushed; 1 teaspoon (each) dried lavender buds, fennel seeds; 2 teaspoons grated and dried orange zest. Makes 1/3 cup. I still used the amount of fennel seeds called for in the recipe even though my herbes de Provence contained some. Enjoy!

