Rating: 4
This was truly outstanding. Personally, I find it's better to stuff the herb/garlic seasoning under the skin as opposed to smearing it on top, as it tends to burn that way so that's what I did. That, and squeezing a lemon half over the top are the only changes I made. Mine was done in 45 minutes in convection, but I did let it come to room temp first. Left it sit tented with foil for about 30 minutes, then poured the juices into a fat separater and darn that was good.